    dc:description "FIGURE 48. Gerromorpha, Veliidae, Rhagovelia trianguloides. A. Apterous male from Itatiaia, Rio de Janeiro (−22.3522, −44.5828). B. Distribution in southeastern Brazil and adjacent areas. Stars indicate new records; circles indicate previous records. Scale bar: 1 mm." ;
